STM_Chen_Luo

Introduction

Core reference: Roberts, M. E., Stewart, B. M., & Tingley, D. (2019). stm: An R package for structural topic models. Journal of Statistical Software, 91(2). https://doi.org/10.18637/jss.v091.i02

This is a tutorial written by Chen Luo for the THUSJC workshop in 2022. If you have any problems, please get in touch with luoc18@mails.tsinghua.edu.cn

The most prominent advantage of stm is it allows researchers to flexibly estimate a topic model that includes document-level metadata.

The primary goal of stm: allow researchers to discover topics and estimate their relationship to document-level metadata.

You can infer not only the document-topic relationship but also the topic-word relationship. In this lecture, we only talk about the former.

Basic concepts Topical prevalence: How much of a document is associated with a topic.

Topical content: The words used within a topic.

There are seven components in the stm process (as illustrated in Figure 2):

ingestion, preparation, estimation, evaluation, understanding, visualization, and extension.

Step 2: 文本的基础处理

  • 特意不使用预处理这一称呼，是为了和之前学习的内容区分开来。这里的基础处理和预处理差别不大，只是面对不同工具时，预处理的步骤有细微差异。
# 查看这一函数的说明
?textProcessor
# 由于我们已经在Python环境中进行了文本预处理，此处需要操作的内容不多
processed <- textProcessor(data$words, # 待处理的列
                           metadata = data, # “元数据”，也即包含所有分析内容的数据
                           lowercase = F, # 需要转化为小写吗？（默认转化）F = FALSE
                           removestopwords = F, # 需要移除停用词吗？停用词来自SMART（默认移除）
                           removepunctuation = F, # 需要移除标点吗？（默认移除）
                           removenumbers = F, # 需要移除数字吗？（默认移除）
                           stem = F, # 需要抽取词干吗？（默认抽取）
                           wordLengths = c(1, Inf), # 词语长度设定，最小的词语长度为1
                           language = "na", # 需要指定语言吗？
                           verbose = T) # 需要查看处理进程吗？

## Creating Output...

Step 3: 正式分析语料准备

  • stm所需的三要素：
  1. document: containing word indices and their associated counts (just like BoW)
  2. vocab: containing the words associated with the word indices (just like dictionary)
  3. metadata: containing document covariates (slightly different with Gensim)
# 编制之后正式分析环节所需语料
?prepDocuments
out <- prepDocuments(processed$documents, # 文档部分
                     processed$vocab, # 词典部分
                     processed$meta, # 元数据部分
                     lower.thresh = 1) # 需要根据词语在文档中的出现情况来筛选词语吗？
## Removing 7413 of 11547 terms (7413 of 34994 tokens) due to frequency 
## Removing 4 Documents with No Words 
## Your corpus now has 1981 documents, 4134 terms and 27581 tokens.
# 额外步骤：判断以上的lower.thresh（阈值）应该如何设定
# How many words and documents would be removed from the dataset at each threshold
?plotRemoved
plotRemoved(processed$documents, 
            lower.thresh = seq(1, 50, by=5)) # 不同的最低阈值设定下，文档、词语的被移除情况

# 将处理好的分析部件分配给变量
docs <- out$documents
vocab <- out$vocab
meta <- out$meta

Step 4: 挑选合适的主题数量

  • 对应参考文献中的Model search across numbers of topics
# searchK uses a data-driven approach to selecting the number of topics
?searchK
# 运行耗时较久
# prevalence can be expressed as a formula that can include multiple covariates and factorial or continuous covariates
set.seed(0330)
kResult <- searchK(docs, # 用来建模的docs
                   vocab, # 词典，既需要docs又需要dict，这和基于LDA的主题建模参数较为接近
                   data = meta, # 元数据对象
                   K = seq(3, 10, 1), # 备择主题数量
                   init.type = "Spectral", # 原始文献中推荐的建模初始化方式
                   prevalence = ~sender, # 带入主题推断过程中的协变量
                   cores = 7, # 运行过程中调用的内核数量
                   verbose = F) # 不输出运行过程的详细信息
## Using multiple-cores.  Progress will not be shown.
# 对上一步的结果进行可视化，来辅助主题数量选择
# Held-out likelihood: the higher the better
# Residuals: the lower the better
# Semantic coherence: the higher the better
# Lower bound: the lower the better
plot(kResult)

Step 5: 正式建模

# 正式建模需要的函数：stm
?stm
fModel <- stm(docs,
              vocab, 
              data = meta,
              K = 5,
              init.type = "Spectral",
              prevalence = ~sender, 
              verbose = F, 
              seed = 20220330)
# 查看正式模型中每个主题下对应的关键词
?labelTopics
labelTopics(fModel, 
            n = 15)

# How to interpret the following output?
# FREX weights words by their overall frequency and how exclusive they are to the topic
# Lift weights words by dividing by their frequency in other topics, therefore giving higher weight to words that appear less frequently in other topics
# Score divides the log frequency of the word in the topic by the log frequency of the word in other topics

Step 6: 执行针对主题偏好的假设检验

  • 对应参考文献中的Estimating metadata/topic relationships
# 估计函数
?estimateEffect
out$meta$sender <- as.factor(out$meta$sender)
estat <- estimateEffect(1:5~sender, # 回归模型的表达式，1:5表示第1个主题-第5个主题
                        fModel, # STM模型本身
                        metadata = meta) # 元数据对象本身
  • 对以上统计结果的可视化处理
plot(estat, 
     covariate = "sender", # 协变量
     topics = seq(1, 5, 1), # DV：每一则主题
     model = fModel, 
     method = "difference", # 估计方法：针对主题偏好的差分方法，类似于t-test
     cov.value1 = "普通用户", # 分类变量-第一类别
     cov.value2 = "认证个人", # 分类变量-第二类别
     xlab = "More like elite user ... More like common user", # X轴标签，需要注意先写value2，后写value1
     xlim = c(-.1, .1), # X轴范围
     labeltype = "custom", # 标签设定方式
     custom.labels = paste("topic", 1:5, sep=" ")) # 自定义标签格式

# 查看具体的回归系数
summary(estat, 
        topics = seq(1, 5, 1))
